@startuml fig4_3_sequence_async_summary
title 图4.3 异步摘要主要时序图（示意）
skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam defaultFontName "Microsoft YaHei"

actor "浏览器" as B
participant "Spring Boot\n Cases API" as A
participant "Redis/DB\n配额与任务" as R
participant "LLM" as L

B -> A : summaryAsync/start(caseId)
A -> R : 校验配额/扣减/写任务
A -> L : 异步生成摘要
L --> A : 摘要文本
A -> R : 更新任务状态 OK/\n失败则回补配额
A --> B : 轮询 status 直至 done/fail
@enduml
